F1GP-Ed is SHAREWARE.  It is not Public Domain.  However, it may be freely
distributed providing:

   (1) None of the distributed files are changed in any way
   (2) F1GP-Ed is not sold for profit and it is not included on any disks
       that are sold solely for profit
   (3) No more than Ł1.50 (inclusive) may be charged for a copy of F1GP-Ed
       by PD libraries
   (4) F1GP-Ed is @{"registered" link "Registration" 0} if it is found to be useful
   (5) Registered user keyfiles are @{b}NOT@{ub} distributed with copies of F1GP-Ed

If F1GP-Ed is to be sold for profit, permission must be obtained from me,
the author (Oliver Roberts).  Included in the above are magazine
coverdisks.

Permission is hereby granted to "F1 Quality Amiga Products/F1GP Amiga Club
Germany" to distribute F1GP-Ed.  Amiga Format magazine has my permission to
distribute the special AF version, obviously.

